            <title>[CASSANDRA-9671] sum() and avg() functions missing for smallint and tinyint types</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9671</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;AggregateFcts&lt;/tt&gt; does not define &lt;tt&gt;sum()&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;avg()&lt;/tt&gt; aggregates for the new &lt;tt&gt;tinyint&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;smallint&lt;/tt&gt; types.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
